# Contact form: submissions are emailed to support@apexmedlaw.com via Formspree.
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io and sign up (free).
# 2. Create a new form and set the notification email to: support@apexmedlaw.com
# 3. Copy your form ID from the form endpoint (e.g. from https://formspree.io/f/xyzabc → xyzabc)
# 4. Create a file named .env in this directory and add:
VITE_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=your_form_id_here
